'''國際足總最佳足球獎'''（'''The Best FIFA Football Awards'''）是由[[國際足總|國際足總]]管理並且每年頒發的年度最大獎項，並從2016年開始頒發。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/the-best-fifa-football-awards/index.html |title=The Best FIFA Football Awards |accessdate=2017-01-11 |archive-date=2020-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213042421/https://www.fifa.com/the-best-fifa-football-awards/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

首屆頒獎儀式於2017年1月9日在[[瑞士|瑞士]]的[[蘇黎世|蘇黎世]]舉行<ref name="circular-1560">{{cite web|title=Circular no. 1560|url=http://resources.fifa.com/mm/document/affederation/administration/02/84/58/20/circularno.1560-thebestfifafootballawardse_neutral.pdf|work=FIFA.com|accessdate=2016-10-24|format=pdf|date=2016-10-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025050426/http://resources.fifa.com/mm/document/affederation/administration/02/84/58/20/circularno.1560-thebestfifafootballawardse_neutral.pdf|archivedate=2016-10-25}}</ref> 該獎項是為了取代原本與法國足球雜誌《法國足球》（France Football），合併頒發的國際足總金球獎，原本的國際足總年度最佳球員（又稱世界足球先生）在2010年與金球獎合併，並且在2016年結束六年的合作夥伴關係。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ballon d'Or vs Best FIFA Men's Player Award|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-4025566/Cristiano-Ronaldo-goes-against-Lionel-Messi-Ballon-d-Best-FIFA-Men-s-Player-Award-come-s-difference.html|work=Dailymail|accessdate=2016-01-02|date=2016-12-12|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812100606/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-4025566/Cristiano-Ronaldo-goes-against-Lionel-Messi-Ballon-d-Best-FIFA-Men-s-Player-Award-come-s-difference.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ballon d'Or and Best FIFA Men's Player awards explained|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11096/10644908/ballon-dor-and-best-fifa-mens-player-awards-explained|work=Sky Sports|accessdate=2016-01-02|date=2016-12-12|archive-date=2016-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216143941/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11096/10644908/ballon-dor-and-best-fifa-mens-player-awards-explained|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此獎項是國際足總對足球領域的個別傑出人物表達最高榮耀的獎項。

